title: Debating the NBA’s Top 25 Players Through 25 Games | Group Chat (Ep. 349)
description:
We review the Lakers vs. Spurs and Thunder vs. Nets games from Tuesday night (1:30) before coming clean on our ballots for The Ringer’s Top 25 Players in the NBA Through 25 Games (31:24).
Hosts: Chris Ryan, Justin Verrier, Haley O’Shaughnessy, Paolo Uggetti
